data.description: This great 3 bed, 1 bath, 1 car garage home sits on more than half an acre and is a short drive from North Pole, Eielson AFB, and Fort Wainwright. This home has a long list of nice upgrades to include all stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen, a tile surround shower/tub, and a newer boiler. The living room is large and great for entertaining company. The open yard allows for ample toy parking as well as enjoying a nice summer day on the back deck. Don’t miss out on this move-in ready home!
